  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Solo Walking Holidays in Europe</h2>
<p><img style="width: 100%; height: auto;" src="/media/13094668/microsoftteams-image-4.png?width=500&amp;height=268.49642004773267" alt="solo walking holiday" data-udi="umb://media/12f21180005949fa8870ec769524049d" /></p>
<div>
<p>Single travellers, this is your call to step into the great outdoors. With each step, you'll uncover new sights, paths and delicious flavours.</p>
<p>Whether you're on the move or unwinding at a relaxing spa, you set the pace.</p>
<p>Not set itineraries, just endless possibilities waiting to be discovered - this is your solo holiday, so walk it your way.</p>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Why book a solo holiday with Inghams?</h2>
<p>Inghams solo walking holidays are designed to give you the perfect mix of activities, exploring and relaxation.</p>
<p>Single travellers will find a community on the move, with a range of group excursions and walking tours. Engage in collective adventures or enjoy the freedom to explore independently - the choice is yours.</p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Friendly in resort reps</h3>
<p><img src="/media/13089978/walkers-mountains-alps-314x193.jpg" alt="Self Guided Walking Holidays" data-udi="umb://media/890f49005ee74077a788bfe55aaa96cd" /></p>
<p>Relax and travel solo without feeling alone. Our Inghams reps are friendly and experienced, so they'll make sure you have everything you need for the ultimate solo holiday.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>Travel solo, your way </h3>
<p><img src="/media/13091814/switzerland-signpost-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/b35fb28d5e294ba8910e960bda65c6f3" /></p>
<p>Our solo walking holidays provide the ideal mix of solitude and exploration, whether you seek an action-packed getaway or a tranquil lakeside retreat.<span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h3>No single supplements </h3>
<p><img src="/media/13091813/women-by-lake-italy-314x193.jpg" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/6982a5908467428ea76300bdb1eb0c48" /></p>
<p>Many of our hotels offer a supplement-free option for travelling solo, or single rooms where you'll be able to enjoy your holiday just like everyone else.<span style="font-weight: 400;"></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h2>Discover our hotels for single travellers</h2>
<p>Get away from it all, and have a holiday to remember. With single travellers in mind, we’ve selected some of the best hotels for people who like to travel alone. From Italy with its stunning lakeside views, to Austria and its majestic mountains, our single-friendly hotels are designed to make you feel at home, with plenty of things to do and see whilst you’re there. </p>
<div>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: left;">Solo holidays in Austria</h3>
</div>
<div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/0e3acebd773c41129a5137bcda17e19c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0e3acebd773c41129a5137bcda17e19c}" title="Alpenhotel Kramerwirt">Alpenhotel, Mayrhofen</a></strong></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13095413/kramerwirt_panorama_whirlpool-1.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="Alpenhotel Kramerwirt" data-udi="umb://media/8846a246b91f4c86b3084e1b0656f2e5" /></p>
<p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">This family run hotel offers exceptional hospitality, comfort and home-style cooking in an Austrian mountain setting. </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/9ed9d1dc5645419e85115978c169b654" href="/{localLink:umb://document/9ed9d1dc5645419e85115978c169b654}" title="Bergresort Seefeld">Bergresort, Seefeld</a></strong></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13095415/sommer-aussenansicht-1-1.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="bergresort, seefeld" data-udi="umb://media/d47d263354f84ce68427a3f167ea5376" /></p>
<p>This hotel in Seefeld features a lovely spa and landscaped gardens, and boasts a distinctive rustic ambiance in its interior design. </p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9}" title="Hotel Mon Repos"></a></div>
<div class="g4">
<p><strong><a data-udi="umb://document/d0764a97320749fe824365958421503b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/d0764a97320749fe824365958421503b}" title="Hotel Saalbacher Hof (Saalbach)">Hotel Saalbacherhof, Saalbach</a></strong></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13095416/hotel-saalbacher-hof.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="hotel saalbacherhof" data-udi="umb://media/a12580093cb84ff29f2ba68f7724902a" /></p>
<p>This hotel is located just 50 metres from the Schattberg and Bernkogel gondolas, so you're perfectly situated to explore all that the resort has to offer. </p>
</div>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: left;">Solo holidays in Switzerland</h3>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/af20be974a1d4650a55baed8aa139e30" href="/{localLink:umb://document/af20be974a1d4650a55baed8aa139e30}" title="Hotel Sunstar Grindelwald"><strong>Hotel Sunstar, Grindelwald</strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13095417/hallenbad-grindelwald-sunstar-alpine-hotel-schweiz-1-1.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="Sunstar hotel grindelwald" data-udi="umb://media/3703b356a2084ca3896f1155702e427a" /></p>
<p>This beautiful wellness hotel offers a range of treatments and activities, with an indoor swimming pool and spa. </p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/8fa1210d0a794f8597980dec5856b80f" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8fa1210d0a794f8597980dec5856b80f}" title="Hotel Alex"><strong>Hotel Alex,</strong><strong> Zermatt</strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13095419/indoor-pool-hotel-alex-zermatt-1.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="Hotel Alex" data-udi="umb://media/18b40558a0394c18acc63d285e8bb729" /></p>
<p>Hotel Alex is a charming hotel offering comfortable and sophisticated rooms, conveniently situated just 2 minutes walk from The Matterhorn Mountain. The hotel offers a large indoor pool, jacuzzi and sauna.</p>
</div>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;"></div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3 style="text-align: left;">Solo holidays in Italy</h3>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/919b13aa1fae4bc68aa9503210e88b44" href="/{localLink:umb://document/919b13aa1fae4bc68aa9503210e88b44}" title="Hotel Adria"><strong>Hotel Adria, Merano</strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13095420/adria-hotel-merano.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="Hotel Adria" data-udi="umb://media/a53674240667434d9b7b9d280b4e36c8" /></p>
<p>This beautiful, Art Nouveau gem is located in Merano's Obermais neighbourhood. It boasts a free wellness centre with an indoor pool, a restaurant, and a complimentary gym.</p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/da18898c2b41431b907c91a66c4f4fc3" href="/{localLink:umb://document/da18898c2b41431b907c91a66c4f4fc3}" title="Hotel Rodella"><strong>Hotel Rodella, Selva</strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13095421/hotel-rodella-selva-21-1.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="Hotel Rodella" data-udi="umb://media/f1bbc73e46bb4a139c27dfa4ebfbfa20" /></p>
<p>You’ll love the hotel’s Natura classification, which means it uses 100% green energy. It also has great facilities and offers a free daily packed lunch.</p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9}" title="Hotel Mon Repos"></a></div>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/cde41f79cd114ef3bf06b1fc5876a3c1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cde41f79cd114ef3bf06b1fc5876a3c1}" title="Hotel Royal Village"><strong>Hotel Royal Village, </strong><strong>Limone</strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13095422/royal-village-pool-1.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="Royal Village Hotel" data-udi="umb://media/468cb6f3b8644c1b9aac69b9d7627e46" /></p>
<p><span>This hotel provides easy access to both Limone and the picturesque lakeside towns, while also boasting breath-taking views of the surrounding mountains and lake from its hilltop location.</span></p>
</div>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;"></div>
<p> </p>
<h3>Solo holidays in Slovenia</h3>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/7705f5943aac4ce4921c9a6b9fd70642" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7705f5943aac4ce4921c9a6b9fd70642}" title="Best Western Hotel Kranjska Gora"><strong>Best Western Hotel, Kranjska Gora </strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13095423/best-western-kranjska-gora-pool-1-1.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="Best Western Hotel" data-udi="umb://media/6c101384c40d4b5589563b1cba887a39" /></p>
<p>This charming hotel is located near Kranjska Gora's town centre and a brief stroll from Lake Jasna, offering a wellness centre with a pool, sauna, and hot tubs, as well as on-site tennis courts.</p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/b27591e078194ddd981ff8e811b26cba" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b27591e078194ddd981ff8e811b26cba}" title="Hotel Kompas"><strong>Hotel Kompas, Kranjska Gora</strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13095424/hotel-kompas.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="Hotel Kompas" data-udi="umb://media/3ae5e7d2bab549c19684dea04b62b3d7" /></p>
<p>This hotel is located amidst lush meadows and is a short distance from the town centre. You can relax and rejuvenate in the luxurious spa, featuring saunas, a Turkish steam room, an indoor pool, and a whirlpool.</p>
</div>
<div style="overflow-x: auto; float: center;"></div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<h3>Solo holidays in France</h3>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/ee980d982293408db473e647a1892aac" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ee980d982293408db473e647a1892aac}" title="Hotel Champs Fleuris"><strong>Hotel Champs Fleuris, Morzine</strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13095425/champs-fleuris-28.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="Hotel Champs Fleuris" data-udi="umb://media/e08d865f19e84862a6b05b704d76e6ce" /></p>
<p>Experience the ultimate in comfort and luxury at this beautiful  hotel, which is known for its delectable cuisine, comfortable rooms, and stunning views of the mountains.</p>
</div>
<div class="g4">
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/29edcd3c50e4458281799c0617b52ba5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/29edcd3c50e4458281799c0617b52ba5}" title="Hotel La Folie Douce"><strong>Hotel La Folie Douce, Chamonix</strong></a></p>
<p><img style="width: 314px; height: 193px;" src="/media/13095426/folie-douce-18-1.jpg?width=314&amp;height=193" alt="Hotel La Folie Douce" data-udi="umb://media/662eec80991a4db6b5259202fa7d066b" /></p>
<p><span>Experience the best views of Chamonix from this hotel, which also features a large spa with a sauna, relaxation room, sun terrace, and steam room.</span></p>
<a data-udi="umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5f65c66796754d4296926388f4150dc9}" title="Hotel Mon Repos"></a></div>
<div class="g4">
<p> </p>
</div>
